name: Highstreet Homes
summary: Welcome to Highstreet Homes, an initial access point to our world. Owner of Highstreet Homes can get access to the world of Highstreet earlier as a home owner, and customize their personal space to their liking. Homes are both accessible via our website at highstreet.market and in VR via SideQuest. We appreciate your support, and if you encounter any issues, feel free to drop by in our discord and ask for help.
